    "We derive the FENNIX small model from the reference one via a knowledge distillation procedure 32, 36 where the distilled model is trained on data labeled with the FeNNix-Bio1(M) model instead of DFT.",
    "This ensures that the forces used in the inner loop of the RESPA scheme are as close to the reference ones as possible, minimizing the correction necessary to recover the correct dynamics and thus the frequency of its application.",
    "In practice, the small model comes in two flavors, either i) as an on-the-fly system-specific model or ii) as a generic model.",
    "We briefly describe here these two distillation strategies.",
    "Specific details about the training parameters can be found in Supporting Information."
